WEBVTT

00:01:35.730 --> 00:01:41.089 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.180 --> 00:01:43.730 line:80%
[Episode 8]

00:02:10.600 --> 00:02:13.240 line:80%
Mr. Sun, please have a seat.

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:14.080 line:80%
Thank you.

00:02:22.170 --> 00:02:23.260 line:80%
So,

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:25.670 line:80%
Yan Zheng was the first human

00:02:25.690 --> 00:02:27.650 line:80%
you treated?

00:02:29.990 --> 00:02:30.760 line:80%
Well...

00:02:31.750 --> 00:02:34.270 line:80%
I couldn't stand aside
and see him die, right?

00:02:34.270 --> 00:02:35.610 line:80%
Actually, I didn't do anything.

00:02:35.610 --> 00:02:37.350 line:80%
He was just lucky.

00:02:39.900 --> 00:02:42.350 line:80%
He was lucky
that he met you when his life was

00:02:42.390 --> 00:02:43.520 line:80%
hanging by a thread.

00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:46.820 line:80%
I'd like to thank you
on Yan Zheng's behalf, Mr. Zhao.

00:02:46.820 --> 00:02:47.780 line:80%
I don't deserve such honor.

00:02:47.780 --> 00:02:48.890 line:80%
I don't deserve it.

00:02:51.020 --> 00:02:52.310 line:80%
Actually, he was

00:02:52.340 --> 00:02:55.830 line:80%
carried back from the wild by my niece.

00:02:55.860 --> 00:02:56.670 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:02:56.690 --> 00:02:59.420 line:80%
he would have frozen to death
in the snow long ago.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:02.110 line:80%
So, there is a story behind it.

00:03:02.130 --> 00:03:02.850 line:80%
Indeed.

00:03:02.880 --> 00:03:05.650 line:80%
Otherwise, the couple
wouldn't have gotten married.

00:03:05.650 --> 00:03:06.780 line:80%
Glad to hear that...

00:03:06.950 --> 00:03:07.640 line:80%
Married?

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:09.690 line:80%
You mean Jiuheng...

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:11.800 line:80%
Well, no.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:13.030 line:80%
You mean Yan Zheng

00:03:13.060 --> 00:03:14.540 line:80%
got married?

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:17.030 line:80%
No, technically,
he's a matrilocal husband.

00:03:17.030 --> 00:03:19.420 line:80%
Zheng married into our family.

00:03:19.950 --> 00:03:21.410 line:80%
Married into your family?

00:03:23.620 --> 00:03:26.480 line:80%
Xie Jiuheng actually became
a matrilocal husband?

00:03:27.020 --> 00:03:28.960 line:80%
Who in the world would dare
make him do that?

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:31.520 line:80%
Even the Emperor wouldn't dare make him
a matrilocal husband.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:33.260 line:80%
He was badly injured back then

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:34.620 line:80%
and couldn't even get out of bed.

00:03:34.620 --> 00:03:37.480 line:80%
It was Changyu who butchered pigs
to earn money

00:03:37.500 --> 00:03:39.370 line:80%
and buy him medicine for treatment.

00:03:39.370 --> 00:03:42.230 line:80%
She saved his life.

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:47.310 line:80%
Mrs. Fan is a butcher?

00:03:47.710 --> 00:03:49.730 line:80%
My sister is amazing.

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:52.690 line:80%
She can knock a pig out
with a single slap.

00:03:54.530 --> 00:03:55.670 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.920 line:80%
I'll ask you one last time.

00:04:00.570 --> 00:04:02.200 line:80%
Will you marry into my family or not?

00:04:02.200 --> 00:04:03.020 line:80%
Let go!

00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:07.610 line:80%
If you refuse,

00:04:08.490 --> 00:04:09.940 line:80%
you'll end up like this.

00:04:12.820 --> 00:04:14.700 line:80%
I'd rather die
than marry into your family!

00:04:14.700 --> 00:04:15.760 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:04:15.780 --> 00:04:19.259 line:80%
Even if you die, you belong to my family!

00:04:24.730 --> 00:04:28.390 line:80%
So Yan Zheng marrying into her family was
taking on a challenge...

00:04:28.410 --> 00:04:30.580 line:80%
No, I mean he was repaying kindness.

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:33.209 line:80%
It wasn't entirely to repay kindness.

00:04:33.830 --> 00:04:36.440 line:80%
The couple is deeply in love.

00:04:36.660 --> 00:04:39.750 line:80%
When Changyu was bullied
by that ingrate Song Yan,

00:04:39.910 --> 00:04:42.340 line:80%
Yan Zheng stood up for her.

00:04:42.830 --> 00:04:43.560 line:80%
Also,

00:04:43.820 --> 00:04:46.810 line:80%
when her uncle tried to seize
her inheritance and house,

00:04:46.810 --> 00:04:49.080 line:80%
it was Yan Zheng who helped out.

00:04:49.590 --> 00:04:51.420 line:80%
My sister's hands got chapped
from working.

00:04:51.420 --> 00:04:52.780 line:80%
Zheng felt bad

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:55.120 line:80%
and bought her balm.

00:04:56.320 --> 00:04:58.880 line:80%
Are you talking about the same person?

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:02.550 line:80%
Did your niece damage Yan Zheng's brain?

00:05:02.630 --> 00:05:03.140 line:80%
Yes...

00:05:04.050 --> 00:05:05.450 line:80%
No, no.

00:05:05.580 --> 00:05:06.980 line:80%
His brain isn't damaged.

00:05:08.980 --> 00:05:10.490 line:80%
When Yan Zheng recovers,

00:05:10.520 --> 00:05:12.280 line:80%
he won't need to work
as an escort anymore.

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:14.080 line:80%
The couple can run the pork stall

00:05:14.100 --> 00:05:16.530 line:80%
and have endless pork for life.

00:05:18.470 --> 00:05:26.620 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:05:23.950 --> 00:05:25.030 line:80%
Wipe my sweat!

00:05:36.760 --> 00:05:39.900 line:80%
Mr. Sun, you saved my niece's husband.

00:05:40.260 --> 00:05:41.770 line:80%
Changyu will be back soon,

00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:43.380 line:80%
and she'll definitely
repay you generously.

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:45.020 line:80%
Changyu is an honest person.

00:05:45.250 --> 00:05:46.920 line:80%
If you show her a little kindness,

00:05:46.920 --> 00:05:48.670 line:80%
she'll return it tenfold.

00:05:49.090 --> 00:05:50.959 line:80%
Benefactor, Chang Yu will surely repay

00:05:50.959 --> 00:05:53.420 line:80%
your great kindness today
when she returns.

00:05:53.430 --> 00:05:54.190 line:80%
Benefactor!

00:05:58.280 --> 00:05:59.550 line:80%
Benefactor!

00:06:05.430 --> 00:06:07.560 line:80%
So you're the one who saved my husband.

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:14.210 line:80%
This pig is for you!

00:06:18.150 --> 00:06:18.960 line:80%
Here you are!

00:06:21.820 --> 00:06:22.740 line:80%
Sir.

00:06:23.490 --> 00:06:24.710 line:80%
-Mr. Sun?
-Mr. Sun.

00:06:25.700 --> 00:06:27.300 line:80%
-Benefactor!
-Benefactor!

00:06:29.490 --> 00:06:31.510 line:80%
Is something wrong?

00:06:32.270 --> 00:06:34.480 line:80%
No, nothing.

00:06:35.190 --> 00:06:36.280 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:06:37.750 --> 00:06:39.070 line:80%
Changyu is back!

00:06:46.310 --> 00:06:47.640 line:80%
Welcome back, Changyu.

00:06:48.180 --> 00:06:49.150 line:80%
-Changyu.
-Uncle.

00:06:49.150 --> 00:06:51.010 line:80%
This is Benefactor Sun,
whom I mentioned to you on the way.

00:06:51.010 --> 00:06:51.610 line:80%
Yes, yes.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:53.110 line:80%
This is the benefactor.

00:06:54.780 --> 00:06:56.150 line:80%
I-I'm flattered.

00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:01.530 line:80%
By the way, Mr. Zhao.

00:07:02.010 --> 00:07:03.160 line:80%
I have a prescription here.

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:04.670 line:80%
It can help Yan Zheng fully recover.

00:07:04.670 --> 00:07:06.260 line:80%
That's wonderful.

00:07:06.320 --> 00:07:07.990 line:80%
I'll go to town right now
to get the medicine.

00:07:07.990 --> 00:07:08.600 line:80%
Let's go quickly.

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:10.800 line:80%
Changyu, we're off to get the medicine.

00:07:12.660 --> 00:07:14.110 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

00:07:14.380 --> 00:07:16.300 line:80%
I should be the one
thanking you, Mrs. Fan.

00:07:16.300 --> 00:07:18.830 line:80%
Thank you
for taking care of him all this time.

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.640 line:80%
Why hasn't he woken up yet?

00:07:30.840 --> 00:07:32.430 line:80%
Is he in a coma?

00:07:32.630 --> 00:07:33.300 line:80%
It's fine.

00:07:33.670 --> 00:07:34.720 line:80%
He took the Nine-turn Pill.

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:35.920 line:80%
It's normal for him to sleep for a while.

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:36.980 line:80%
He'll wake up soon.

00:07:41.520 --> 00:07:42.580 line:80%
Please take a seat.

00:07:45.209 --> 00:07:46.280 line:80%
Have some tea, please.

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:46.910 line:80%
Thank you.

00:07:56.390 --> 00:07:57.730 line:80%
Are you his master?

00:07:58.880 --> 00:08:00.810 line:80%
Yan Zheng has no master.

00:08:01.710 --> 00:08:04.670 line:80%
No one in this world would dare
to be his master.

00:08:08.180 --> 00:08:09.840 line:80%
Then you're his close friend?

00:08:12.130 --> 00:08:14.110 line:80%
Before I came, I thought I was.

00:08:14.190 --> 00:08:15.400 line:80%
But now that I'm here,

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:17.160 line:80%
I found out that this man
didn't even tell me

00:08:17.160 --> 00:08:19.620 line:80%
about something as important
as getting married.

00:08:19.620 --> 00:08:21.550 line:80%
So I'm not sure anymore.

00:08:21.870 --> 00:08:23.130 line:80%
It happened suddenly.

00:08:23.540 --> 00:08:25.250 line:80%
It's not entirely his fault.

00:08:27.690 --> 00:08:29.420 line:80%
I begged him.

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:33.359 line:80%
You begged him to be
your matrilocal husband,

00:08:33.359 --> 00:08:34.380 line:80%
and he agreed?

00:08:36.430 --> 00:08:37.380 line:80%
Sort of.

00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:41.240 line:80%
It turns out all those noble ladies
in the capital

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:43.170 line:80%
lost because they didn't speak up.

00:08:43.839 --> 00:08:47.010 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:08:58.110 --> 00:08:59.820 line:80%
What exactly happened recently?

00:08:59.820 --> 00:09:02.340 line:80%
How did you end up
with that female butcher?

00:09:03.830 --> 00:09:05.210 line:80%
I was secretly investigating

00:09:05.210 --> 00:09:07.140 line:80%
the Jinzhou case from 16 years ago.

00:09:07.530 --> 00:09:09.590 line:80%
But on the battlefield in Chongzhou,

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:11.770 line:80%
I was shot by a hidden arrow.

00:09:24.610 --> 00:09:25.970 line:80%
Xie Yi and Xie San

00:09:27.090 --> 00:09:29.750 line:80%
desperately fought their way
out of the ambush,

00:09:30.400 --> 00:09:33.000 line:80%
but ended up being hacked to death
by the enemy.

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:43.920 line:80%
I drifted down the river to Jizhou.

00:10:56.360 --> 00:10:58.290 line:80%
In the end, I collapsed in the snow.

00:10:59.410 --> 00:11:00.560 line:80%
She saved me.

00:11:02.520 --> 00:11:04.270 line:80%
Who on earth wanted you dead?

00:11:05.570 --> 00:11:07.100 line:80%
There's no solid proof yet,

00:11:08.050 --> 00:11:09.720 line:80%
but I have a pretty good guess.

00:11:10.590 --> 00:11:12.720 line:80%
Should we contact your uncle for help?

00:11:22.470 --> 00:11:23.920 line:80%
No way.

00:11:24.190 --> 00:11:25.460 line:80%
Was it...

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:28.260 line:80%
Was it Prime Minister Wei
who wanted to kill you?

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:30.040 line:80%
He raised you from childhood

00:11:30.070 --> 00:11:31.560 line:80%
and found the best teachers
to educate you.

00:11:31.560 --> 00:11:32.240 line:80%
Why...

00:11:37.940 --> 00:11:40.540 line:80%
What reason would he possibly have
to kill you?

00:11:41.290 --> 00:11:42.740 line:80%
I want to know, too.

00:11:44.670 --> 00:11:45.830 line:80%
Right when I happened to be investigating

00:11:45.830 --> 00:11:47.760 line:80%
the Jinzhou case from 16 years ago,

00:11:48.830 --> 00:11:50.830 line:80%
he just couldn't wait to make a move.

00:11:51.780 --> 00:11:54.100 line:80%
I found this the day
the Fan's house was attacked.

00:11:54.100 --> 00:11:55.710 line:80%
The Wei family's Iron Suicide Warriors.

00:11:55.710 --> 00:11:57.240 line:80%
Seventeen of them in total.

00:11:58.510 --> 00:12:00.000 line:80%
I've heard that the Wei family has

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:02.390 line:80%
four ranks of Suicide Warriors—
Heaven, Earth, Dark, and Yellow.

00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:03.800 line:80%
If he wanted to kill you,

00:12:04.070 --> 00:12:05.400 line:80%
sending only
a few Dark-rank Suicide Warriors

00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:06.530 line:80%
would not be enough.

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:08.470 line:80%
Then they came for Mrs. Fan?

00:12:09.630 --> 00:12:11.160 line:80%
That makes even less sense.

00:12:11.410 --> 00:12:13.710 line:80%
Mrs. Fan's family are
just ordinary people.

00:12:13.710 --> 00:12:16.190 line:80%
How could they have grudges
against the Prime Minister?

00:12:16.190 --> 00:12:17.470 line:80%
It is indeed fishy.

00:12:18.270 --> 00:12:20.070 line:80%
They ransacked the Fan's house,

00:12:20.310 --> 00:12:23.310 line:80%
seemingly looking for something.

00:12:25.110 --> 00:12:26.570 line:80%
Looking for something?

00:12:27.170 --> 00:12:28.240 line:80%
The Fan's house...

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:30.830 line:80%
All these unsolved cases are

00:12:30.830 --> 00:12:32.690 line:80%
tangled like a messy ball of yarn.

00:12:34.050 --> 00:12:35.160 line:80%
But you found the thread

00:12:35.160 --> 00:12:36.890 line:80%
immediately

00:12:36.920 --> 00:12:39.180 line:80%
and traced it directly to the Fan family.

00:12:39.410 --> 00:12:41.120 line:80%
As expected of you, Xie Jiuheng.

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:43.030 line:80%
I didn't find the thread.

00:12:44.710 --> 00:12:46.310 line:80%
She just happened to save me.

00:13:12.770 --> 00:13:13.900 line:80%
No, don't look back.

00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:21.740 line:80%
Done.

00:13:22.190 --> 00:13:23.830 line:80%
Hello, Mr. Sun.

00:13:23.960 --> 00:13:24.770 line:80%
Hello.

00:13:26.580 --> 00:13:27.830 line:80%
Changning, you just look

00:13:27.830 --> 00:13:29.560 line:80%
like a kind and sensible child,

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:31.120 line:80%
feeding the rabbits

00:13:31.120 --> 00:13:32.180 line:80%
and the chicken...

00:13:35.100 --> 00:13:36.230 line:80%
Gyrfalcon?

00:13:37.970 --> 00:13:40.700 line:80%
Mr. Sun, you saved
my sister and brother-in-law.

00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:42.550 line:80%
You are our benefactor.

00:13:42.960 --> 00:13:44.750 line:80%
The falcon saved me.

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:47.020 line:80%
So it is a benefactor bird.

00:13:47.050 --> 00:13:49.460 line:80%
So the rabbits need to grow up quickly.

00:13:49.550 --> 00:13:52.550 line:80%
Then the falcon can eat them later.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.610 line:80%
Your brother-in-law saved you, too.

00:14:05.610 --> 00:14:06.770 line:80%
How will you repay him?

00:14:06.770 --> 00:14:09.480 line:80%
When Zheng and Changyu have a baby,

00:14:09.550 --> 00:14:11.750 line:80%
I'll teach the baby how to butcher pigs.

00:14:12.280 --> 00:14:14.350 line:80%
Changning, stop playing with the rabbits.

00:14:14.350 --> 00:14:16.210 line:80%
Remember to wash the vegetables.

00:14:17.470 --> 00:14:18.470 line:80%
Mr. Sun?

00:14:18.910 --> 00:14:19.570 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:14:20.420 --> 00:14:22.330 line:80%
We can't have a guest do chores.

00:14:22.350 --> 00:14:23.230 line:80%
It's fine!

00:14:23.260 --> 00:14:24.920 line:80%
I can't eat your food for free.

00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:26.750 line:80%
Thank you, then.

00:14:26.850 --> 00:14:27.510 line:80%
No problem.

00:14:29.950 --> 00:14:32.770 line:80%
I have to make Yan Zheng owe me this one.

00:14:32.840 --> 00:14:34.330 line:80%
When we get back to Luyuan,

00:14:34.360 --> 00:14:36.360 line:80%
I'll make him repay me for this meal.

00:14:41.270 --> 00:14:43.400 line:80%
Yan Zheng is also going back to Luyuan?

00:14:46.780 --> 00:14:47.500 line:80%
He...

00:14:48.740 --> 00:14:50.870 line:80%
He still has many unfulfilled wishes.

00:14:50.990 --> 00:14:53.120 line:80%
He will definitely leave afterwards.

00:14:53.530 --> 00:14:54.270 line:80%
Didn't he

00:14:54.720 --> 00:14:56.030 line:80%
tell you?

00:14:56.380 --> 00:14:57.560 line:80%
After I recover,

00:14:58.130 --> 00:14:59.410 line:80%
I will leave.

00:15:00.410 --> 00:15:02.010 line:80%
I won't overstay my welcome.

00:15:05.070 --> 00:15:05.880 line:80%
He did.

00:15:06.840 --> 00:15:07.900 line:80%
He did tell me that.

00:15:09.850 --> 00:15:10.600 line:80%
That's good.

00:15:37.550 --> 00:15:38.210 line:80%
Did you

00:15:38.530 --> 00:15:40.590 line:80%
really fall for that female butcher?

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:44.240 line:80%
Alright, alright.

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:45.430 line:80%
I'll stop asking.

00:15:47.710 --> 00:15:50.370 line:80%
You were still acting tough
in court yesterday.

00:15:50.390 --> 00:15:51.920 line:80%
If I hadn't arrived in time,

00:15:52.050 --> 00:15:54.910 line:80%
you'd have been totally screwed
by now, I'm afraid.

00:15:54.980 --> 00:15:56.580 line:80%
It was all for her, wasn't it?

00:16:05.450 --> 00:16:06.960 line:80%
In my current situation,

00:16:07.810 --> 00:16:10.070 line:80%
with my national
and family vengeance unresolved,

00:16:10.070 --> 00:16:11.910 line:80%
and with my serious injuries
still unhealed,

00:16:11.910 --> 00:16:14.910 line:80%
falling for someone
would only bring them disasters.

00:16:15.570 --> 00:16:16.520 line:80%
If you were me,

00:16:18.490 --> 00:16:20.690 line:80%
would you let yourself fall in love now?

00:16:25.240 --> 00:16:26.160 line:80%
Humans are

00:16:27.530 --> 00:16:30.130 line:80%
not deities
who cut off emotions and desires.

00:16:31.310 --> 00:16:32.470 line:80%
It's hard to control

00:16:34.520 --> 00:16:35.740 line:80%
your feelings.

00:16:42.050 --> 00:16:43.450 line:80%
You should go back early.

00:16:43.730 --> 00:16:46.010 line:80%
Secretly investigate
Wei Yan's movements for me.

00:16:46.010 --> 00:16:48.900 line:80%
The situation on the battlefield is
shifting rapidly.

00:16:48.900 --> 00:16:51.960 line:80%
With that coward Wei Xuan
commanding the Three Armies,

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:54.990 line:80%
the situation in the Northwest will surely
undergo drastic changes.

00:16:54.990 --> 00:16:56.790 line:80%
The time I can hide my identity is

00:16:57.330 --> 00:16:58.060 line:80%
running out.

00:16:58.920 --> 00:17:01.160 line:80%
Prince Changxin will definitely
march south.

00:17:01.160 --> 00:17:02.160 line:80%
And Old General He

00:17:02.950 --> 00:17:05.000 line:80%
will surely be unable to hold out alone.

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:07.930 line:80%
Why don't you leave with me tomorrow,
Your Lordship?

00:17:32.070 --> 00:17:32.930 line:80%
Changyu,

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:35.520 line:80%
the government has already
closed your family's case.

00:17:34.140 --> 00:17:39.290 line:80%
[Qingping County Government Office]

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:38.350 line:80%
Mr. Wang,

00:17:38.520 --> 00:17:40.040 line:80%
we haven't found the mastermind yet.

00:17:40.040 --> 00:17:42.300 line:80%
How could they close the case so hastily?

00:17:42.660 --> 00:17:43.960 line:80%
The people who died
in the pine forest were

00:17:43.960 --> 00:17:44.830 line:80%
the culprits.

00:17:45.610 --> 00:17:48.310 line:80%
They were bandits
from the Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:17:48.310 --> 00:17:49.780 line:80%
How could it be bandits?

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:53.080 line:80%
Why would bandits ransack my home?

00:17:53.590 --> 00:17:54.780 line:80%
I was thinking,

00:17:54.800 --> 00:17:57.720 line:80%
perhaps when your father worked
as an escort years ago,

00:17:57.720 --> 00:17:59.170 line:80%
he offended someone.

00:18:00.490 --> 00:18:02.150 line:80%
Changyu, listen to my advice.

00:18:02.330 --> 00:18:04.840 line:80%
Sell your pigsty, house, and land,

00:18:05.320 --> 00:18:07.450 line:80%
and go hide somewhere else for a while.

00:18:09.700 --> 00:18:10.860 line:80%
Father, Mother.

00:18:12.670 --> 00:18:13.800 line:80%
Tell me,

00:18:14.040 --> 00:18:15.700 line:80%
should I take Changning away?

00:18:17.870 --> 00:18:18.990 line:80%
Do you think

00:18:19.040 --> 00:18:20.630 line:80%
Yan Zheng will go with me?

00:18:24.650 --> 00:18:27.180 line:80%
I'm afraid I've got him
caught up in this mess.

00:18:33.200 --> 00:18:33.960 line:80%
Changyu.

00:18:34.650 --> 00:18:36.380 line:80%
Why are you sitting here alone?

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:38.020 line:80%
What's wrong, Mrs. Wang?

00:18:38.020 --> 00:18:40.080 line:80%
Did a rich relative visit your place?

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:40.790 line:80%
Why?

00:18:40.830 --> 00:18:41.800 line:80%
I just saw the carriage

00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:43.350 line:80%
that left your house.

00:18:43.350 --> 00:18:46.610 line:80%
It was even grander
than the Song family's when they moved.

00:18:50.600 --> 00:18:52.290 line:80%
The basket! Your basket!

00:19:40.760 --> 00:19:42.430 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:19:45.720 --> 00:19:46.390 line:80%
[Today, I'm bidding a farewell
to you, Mrs. Fan.]

00:19:46.150 --> 00:19:46.830 line:80%
Today...

00:19:46.420 --> 00:19:47.180 line:80%
[Wish you a peaceful life,
year after year. Best regards.]

00:19:47.590 --> 00:19:48.480 line:80%
Bid...

00:19:49.120 --> 00:19:50.750 line:80%
A farewell to you, Mrs. Fan.

00:19:51.510 --> 00:19:52.910 line:80%
Wish you a peaceful life.

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:11.150 line:80%
Changyu.

00:20:12.550 --> 00:20:13.670 line:80%
Did Zheng leave?

00:20:18.640 --> 00:20:20.040 line:80%
It's good that he's gone.

00:20:20.930 --> 00:20:21.760 line:80%
That's good.

00:20:22.830 --> 00:20:24.800 line:80%
If there's any more trouble in the future,

00:20:24.800 --> 00:20:26.330 line:80%
he won't be dragged into it.

00:20:29.610 --> 00:20:31.150 line:80%
Why didn't he say goodbye?

00:20:36.130 --> 00:20:37.800 line:80%
Zheng is back.

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:55.570 line:80%
Yan Zheng, you...

00:20:57.800 --> 00:21:00.140 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:21:00.520 --> 00:21:03.980 line:80%
Zheng went to Mrs. Zhuang's place
to read a letter for the old lady.

00:21:01.070 --> 00:21:02.400 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:21:03.310 --> 00:21:06.140 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:21:05.790 --> 00:21:07.070 line:80%
She has trouble walking,

00:21:06.490 --> 00:21:09.070 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:21:07.100 --> 00:21:09.630 line:80%
so I went over there
to read the letter for her.

00:21:09.730 --> 00:21:11.370 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:21:11.890 --> 00:21:16.190 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:13.800 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:21:14.520 --> 00:21:15.380 line:80%
Are you crying?

00:21:17.910 --> 00:21:19.150 line:80%
No way.

00:21:19.580 --> 00:21:21.980 line:80%
The smoke from the cured meat
got in my eyes.

00:21:25.350 --> 00:21:26.440 line:80%
Sun has left.

00:21:26.720 --> 00:21:27.910 line:80%
He left some money.

00:21:32.070 --> 00:21:34.870 line:80%
Mr. Sun likes things tidy.

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:35.830 line:80%
Before he left,

00:21:35.830 --> 00:21:38.350 line:80%
he cleaned the house thoroughly.

00:21:45.310 --> 00:21:47.520 line:80%
I came to look for straw ropes

00:21:47.540 --> 00:21:48.800 line:80%
to hang the cured meat.

00:22:11.850 --> 00:22:13.050 line:80%
Why did I take a chain?

00:22:17.520 --> 00:22:18.610 line:80%
To make cured meat,

00:22:18.680 --> 00:22:20.800 line:80%
you need to salt it for 7 to 8 days,

00:22:20.800 --> 00:22:22.550 line:80%
and then smoke it with cypress branches.

00:22:22.550 --> 00:22:24.590 line:80%
That way, the meat lasts longer.

00:22:24.710 --> 00:22:25.360 line:80%
Look,

00:22:26.040 --> 00:22:27.800 line:80%
the meat I smoked a few days ago is

00:22:27.800 --> 00:22:29.200 line:80%
ready to eat now.

00:22:29.310 --> 00:22:31.520 line:80%
I'll send some to Grandfather tomorrow.

00:22:31.520 --> 00:22:34.450 line:80%
The medicine is on the table.
Drink it while it's hot.

00:22:34.680 --> 00:22:35.270 line:80%
Okay.

00:22:38.610 --> 00:22:40.520 line:80%
I went to the magistrate's office today.

00:22:40.520 --> 00:22:42.550 line:80%
Mr. Wang said the case is closed.

00:22:43.630 --> 00:22:44.800 line:80%
But we still

00:22:44.960 --> 00:22:47.240 line:80%
don't know if those people were

00:22:47.350 --> 00:22:48.960 line:80%
after money or revenge.

00:22:51.830 --> 00:22:53.350 line:80%
If it's for revenge,

00:22:54.070 --> 00:22:56.200 line:80%
they will definitely come back again.

00:22:57.050 --> 00:22:58.250 line:80%
What do you plan to do?

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:02.720 line:80%
I plan to sell the property
after the festival

00:23:03.280 --> 00:23:05.680 line:80%
and take Changning away
to hide for a while.

00:23:08.110 --> 00:23:10.440 line:80%
If you're leaving, the sooner the better.

00:23:11.520 --> 00:23:13.160 line:80%
But it's almost New Year,

00:23:13.240 --> 00:23:14.700 line:80%
and it's snowing outside.

00:23:15.520 --> 00:23:17.150 line:80%
The paperwork for selling the property

00:23:17.150 --> 00:23:18.950 line:80%
will take some time to transfer.

00:23:19.240 --> 00:23:20.390 line:80%
In a few days,

00:23:20.520 --> 00:23:22.580 line:80%
your injury will also heal a bit more.

00:23:22.630 --> 00:23:23.630 line:80%
What do you think?

00:23:26.310 --> 00:23:26.960 line:80%
Me?

00:23:28.680 --> 00:23:30.950 line:80%
Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao are
really nice people.

00:23:30.950 --> 00:23:33.910 line:80%
Their son died outside in the war.

00:23:34.070 --> 00:23:36.530 line:80%
I want to leave my fields
to them for farming.

00:23:36.820 --> 00:23:39.750 line:80%
Also, I'll write the divorce paper
for you in advance

00:23:39.990 --> 00:23:42.520 line:80%
and leave you some money
for travel expenses.

00:23:44.760 --> 00:23:45.960 line:80%
I have my own plans.

00:23:46.990 --> 00:23:48.790 line:80%
You don't need to worry about me.

00:23:49.620 --> 00:23:51.230 line:80%
Then will you go with me?

00:23:55.930 --> 00:23:58.690 line:80%
Or do you want to stay here to heal?

00:24:02.350 --> 00:24:03.280 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:10.170 line:80%
Then help me hang the cured meat, too.

00:24:29.850 --> 00:24:31.160 line:80%
Did your parents leave
any inheritance behind

00:24:31.160 --> 00:24:33.400 line:80%
that you want to take with you?

00:24:36.960 --> 00:24:37.630 line:80%
Yes.

00:24:40.870 --> 00:24:41.930 line:80%
My butcher knives.

00:24:42.110 --> 00:24:44.470 line:80%
I take that set with me wherever I go.

00:24:44.660 --> 00:24:46.990 line:80%
With them,
I can butcher pigs for a living.

00:24:47.310 --> 00:24:49.240 line:80%
If we run into hooligans on the way,

00:24:49.280 --> 00:24:50.900 line:80%
I can also use them to defend us.

00:24:50.900 --> 00:24:51.760 line:80%
Anything else?

00:24:53.570 --> 00:24:54.430 line:80%
The title deed!

00:24:55.200 --> 00:24:56.820 line:80%
Since the case is closed,

00:24:57.070 --> 00:24:58.600 line:80%
I'll take it out in a moment.

00:24:59.250 --> 00:25:00.250 line:80%
The title deed...

00:25:01.510 --> 00:25:03.710 line:80%
Did your parents ever mention anything

00:25:04.110 --> 00:25:05.150 line:80%
that you must take with you,

00:25:05.150 --> 00:25:07.390 line:80%
even if you're running for your life?

00:25:10.720 --> 00:25:11.310 line:80%
Yes.

00:25:11.350 --> 00:25:12.000 line:80%
What is it?

00:25:12.550 --> 00:25:13.200 line:80%
My sister.

00:25:22.440 --> 00:25:23.280 line:80%
Darn it...

00:25:28.070 --> 00:25:28.910 line:80%
Tangerine peel candy.

00:25:28.910 --> 00:25:29.910 line:80%
I've tasted it.

00:25:29.910 --> 00:25:32.910 line:80%
It's sweet and sour,
and it helps with the bitterness.

00:25:33.700 --> 00:25:34.380 line:80%
Thank you.

00:25:44.240 --> 00:25:46.240 line:80%
That girl is a real jinx.

00:25:47.720 --> 00:25:49.640 line:80%
She not only brought about
her parents' deaths

00:25:49.640 --> 00:25:51.650 line:80%
but also implicated her uncle.

00:25:51.450 --> 00:25:53.980 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Daniu]

00:25:51.780 --> 00:25:53.880 line:80%
How did Fan Daniu

00:25:54.040 --> 00:25:56.070 line:80%
end up being killed by bandits?

00:25:56.870 --> 00:25:57.910 line:80%
Maybe

00:25:57.930 --> 00:26:00.720 line:80%
Fan Changyu paid someone to kill him.

00:26:00.750 --> 00:26:02.500 line:80%
Shut up, Granny Kang.

00:26:02.910 --> 00:26:05.110 line:80%
Save some karma for your two grandsons.

00:26:05.230 --> 00:26:07.360 line:80%
What? Your eldest son died,

00:26:07.390 --> 00:26:08.820 line:80%
and your daughter-in-law
ran off with someone.

00:26:08.820 --> 00:26:10.890 line:80%
Are you also a jinx,
having caused all these?

00:26:10.890 --> 00:26:12.700 line:80%
You... You're full of crap!

00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:15.770 line:80%
Changyu.

00:26:16.990 --> 00:26:17.920 line:80%
Changyu is here.

00:26:20.760 --> 00:26:22.350 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:26:23.590 --> 00:26:24.960 line:80%
Fan Changyu,

00:26:25.390 --> 00:26:27.120 line:80%
how dare you show up here again?

00:26:28.760 --> 00:26:31.250 line:80%
You brat! I'm going to beat you to death!

00:26:36.590 --> 00:26:37.350 line:80%
How could Changyu

00:26:37.350 --> 00:26:38.070 line:80%
fight her?

00:26:38.070 --> 00:26:39.270 line:80%
She's way out of line!

00:26:39.830 --> 00:26:40.390 line:80%
Changyu.

00:26:40.390 --> 00:26:41.750 line:80%
You jinx!

00:26:41.870 --> 00:26:42.280 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:26:42.280 --> 00:26:44.000 line:80%
Getting Fan Daniu killed wasn't enough,

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:45.390 line:80%
and now you dare come to my house?

00:26:45.390 --> 00:26:47.100 line:80%
I'll teach you a lesson!

00:26:49.240 --> 00:26:49.870 line:80%
I came

00:26:50.480 --> 00:26:52.480 line:80%
to bring something to Grandfather.

00:26:52.910 --> 00:26:54.640 line:80%
I'm not here to stir up trouble.

00:26:54.830 --> 00:26:56.230 line:80%
If you go past this blade,

00:26:56.960 --> 00:26:58.760 line:80%
I'll cut out your filthy tongue.

00:27:00.590 --> 00:27:01.650 line:80%
What does she mean?

00:27:01.720 --> 00:27:02.850 line:80%
She's too arrogant.

00:27:03.880 --> 00:27:04.680 line:80%
Grandfather.

00:27:05.750 --> 00:27:07.410 line:80%
I brought you some cured meat.

00:27:07.480 --> 00:27:08.680 line:80%
Oh, Changyu.

00:27:12.800 --> 00:27:13.930 line:80%
How are you feeling?

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:16.770 line:80%
Had anyone bullied you?

00:27:16.800 --> 00:27:17.680 line:80%
No.

00:27:18.200 --> 00:27:19.520 line:80%
No one bullies me.

00:27:20.630 --> 00:27:21.550 line:80%
Changyu,

00:27:22.590 --> 00:27:25.390 line:80%
Daniu and Erniu are both gone.

00:27:26.900 --> 00:27:28.140 line:80%
There is something

00:27:28.760 --> 00:27:30.990 line:80%
I can't take to my grave.

00:27:31.870 --> 00:27:35.240 line:80%
-In fact, your father is my...
-It was her father,

00:27:35.240 --> 00:27:36.350 line:80%
Fan Erniu!

00:27:36.890 --> 00:27:38.310 line:80%
Ever since they came home,

00:27:38.310 --> 00:27:40.260 line:80%
we haven't had a single good day.

00:27:40.390 --> 00:27:43.820 line:80%
My Daniu was cursed to death
because of their family.

00:27:45.200 --> 00:27:46.920 line:80%
Sooner or later, our whole family

00:27:46.920 --> 00:27:48.860 line:80%
will die because of her!

00:27:51.520 --> 00:27:53.750 line:80%
Grandfather, take care of yourself.

00:27:53.780 --> 00:27:54.910 line:80%
I'm taking my leave.

00:27:55.080 --> 00:27:56.610 line:80%
I'll visit you another day.

00:28:10.310 --> 00:28:11.710 line:80%
Look at her! Look!

00:28:11.760 --> 00:28:12.700 line:80%
This girl.

00:28:12.870 --> 00:28:15.600 line:80%
She doesn't even
pay respects to her uncle!

00:28:18.430 --> 00:28:20.770 line:80%
It's karma...

00:28:26.750 --> 00:28:29.210 line:80%
[South Market]

00:28:29.330 --> 00:28:31.710 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:28:31.710 --> 00:28:38.090 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:28:36.720 --> 00:28:37.440 line:80%
Changyu.

00:28:39.350 --> 00:28:40.790 line:80%
Closing up so early?

00:28:41.480 --> 00:28:43.740 line:80%
Mr. Li, I'm not doing business today.

00:28:43.760 --> 00:28:45.170 line:80%
Not even with me?

00:28:46.800 --> 00:28:48.400 line:80%
Something happened at home.

00:28:49.480 --> 00:28:52.500 line:80%
I don't plan to open the shop
until the end of the year.

00:28:52.590 --> 00:28:54.380 line:80%
I'm not here to buy meat today.

00:28:54.590 --> 00:28:56.250 line:80%
Our manager wants to see you.

00:28:57.780 --> 00:29:01.960 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:28:58.320 --> 00:28:59.380 line:80%
Sir,

00:28:59.720 --> 00:29:00.630 line:80%
welcome.

00:29:03.370 --> 00:29:04.460 line:80%
You're back.

00:29:06.550 --> 00:29:07.590 line:80%
Take care, sir and madam.

00:29:07.590 --> 00:29:09.210 line:80%
Changyu, look.

00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:12.140 line:80%
This is the main hall
of our Yixiang Restaurant.

00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:13.030 line:80%
Take a look.

00:29:13.050 --> 00:29:14.250 line:80%
It's so magnificent.

00:29:14.710 --> 00:29:15.540 line:80%
Of course.

00:29:16.210 --> 00:29:18.390 line:80%
It's the best in Lin'an.

00:29:19.510 --> 00:29:20.880 line:80%
It's actually not busy right now.

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:22.170 line:80%
During festivals,

00:29:22.250 --> 00:29:24.170 line:80%
it's so crowded
that there's almost nowhere to stand.

00:29:24.170 --> 00:29:25.170 line:80%
It's so bustling!

00:29:27.680 --> 00:29:28.480 line:80%
Welcome back.

00:29:30.720 --> 00:29:31.900 line:80%
It's huge.

00:29:32.110 --> 00:29:34.170 line:80%
Come on, Changyu. It's just up ahead.

00:29:35.800 --> 00:29:36.960 line:80%
I'll leave you here.

00:29:37.110 --> 00:29:38.060 line:80%
The manager is inside.

00:29:38.060 --> 00:29:39.020 line:80%
Go on in.

00:30:19.770 --> 00:30:21.900 line:80%
Manager, Mrs. Fan is here.

00:30:25.280 --> 00:30:26.750 line:80%
Changyu, is it you?

00:30:42.340 --> 00:30:45.930 line:80%
So you are the manager
of Yixiang Restaurant.

00:30:46.240 --> 00:30:47.570 line:80%
I always thought

00:30:48.070 --> 00:30:50.250 line:80%
the manager here was a man.

00:30:51.760 --> 00:30:53.300 line:80%
Before I met you,

00:30:53.320 --> 00:30:54.000 line:80%
I also never thought

00:30:54.000 --> 00:30:55.390 line:80%
a lady who butchers pigs

00:30:55.410 --> 00:30:56.890 line:80%
would be so beautiful.

00:30:57.940 --> 00:30:59.980 line:80%
You are the beautiful one.

00:31:02.030 --> 00:31:03.850 line:80%
My surname is Yu,
and my given name is Qianqian.

00:31:03.850 --> 00:31:05.510 line:80%
I'm a few years older than you,

00:31:06.070 --> 00:31:09.100 line:80%
so I'll take the liberty
of calling you Changyu.

00:31:09.240 --> 00:31:10.740 line:80%
I heard from Mr. Li

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:12.480 line:80%
that you can not only butcher pigs,

00:31:12.480 --> 00:31:15.080 line:80%
but also make
really delectable braised meat.

00:31:15.130 --> 00:31:17.010 line:80%
Thank you for the compliment, Manager.

00:31:17.010 --> 00:31:18.790 line:80%
Don't be modest.

00:31:19.310 --> 00:31:20.670 line:80%
I saw

00:31:20.700 --> 00:31:23.830 line:80%
you smash the signboard
of the Wang's Braised Meat Shop.

00:31:25.850 --> 00:31:27.570 line:80%
I did smash it,

00:31:28.130 --> 00:31:29.710 line:80%
but I didn't start it.

00:31:30.110 --> 00:31:31.830 line:80%
It doesn't matter who started it.

00:31:31.830 --> 00:31:33.960 line:80%
You were right to smash their signboard.

00:31:33.960 --> 00:31:35.760 line:80%
Ever since the Young Master of the Wang's

00:31:35.760 --> 00:31:37.630 line:80%
took over the Wang's Braised Meat Shop,

00:31:37.630 --> 00:31:38.760 line:80%
he's been dishonest in business

00:31:38.760 --> 00:31:40.070 line:80%
and handsy during interactions.

00:31:40.070 --> 00:31:42.800 line:80%
I've long wanted
to end my partnership with them.

00:31:44.720 --> 00:31:45.650 line:80%
Bring it up here.

00:31:48.630 --> 00:31:49.520 line:80%
Bring it in.

00:31:54.720 --> 00:31:55.870 line:80%
To be honest with you,

00:31:55.870 --> 00:31:58.470 line:80%
I had someone buy your braised meat
for 10 days.

00:31:58.830 --> 00:31:59.680 line:80%
The consistent quality

00:31:59.680 --> 00:32:00.880 line:80%
and the same portions

00:32:01.000 --> 00:32:03.400 line:80%
proved that you truly are
an honest person.

00:32:03.480 --> 00:32:05.350 line:80%
That's how we're supposed to do business.

00:32:05.350 --> 00:32:06.350 line:80%
My father said,

00:32:06.430 --> 00:32:08.630 line:80%
"Dishonest business won't last long."

00:32:08.720 --> 00:32:12.390 line:80%
So, regarding the braised meat business,

00:32:13.520 --> 00:32:14.780 line:80%
I want to work with you.

00:32:17.350 --> 00:32:19.660 line:80%
Thank you for your appreciation, Manager.

00:32:19.660 --> 00:32:22.290 line:80%
But I can't make this deal with you.

00:32:22.830 --> 00:32:23.590 line:80%
Why?

00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:25.860 line:80%
Something happened in my family.

00:32:25.970 --> 00:32:28.300 line:80%
I'll be leaving Lin'an after the New Year.

00:32:31.760 --> 00:32:33.030 line:80%
In this case,

00:32:33.350 --> 00:32:35.830 line:80%
the town will lose your delicious dishes.

00:32:39.350 --> 00:32:41.080 line:80%
If you really like it, Manager,

00:32:41.590 --> 00:32:44.250 line:80%
I can tell you the ingredients
and how to make it.

00:32:45.120 --> 00:32:48.250 line:80%
You can just have your staff
make it following my recipe.

00:32:53.590 --> 00:32:55.620 line:80%
You are such a straightforward girl!

00:32:55.620 --> 00:32:56.870 line:80%
I've only chatted with you for a bit,

00:32:56.870 --> 00:32:59.390 line:80%
and you've already
given your secret recipe away.

00:32:59.390 --> 00:33:00.630 line:80%
If you go somewhere far from home,

00:33:00.630 --> 00:33:02.490 line:80%
you must keep your wits about you.

00:33:03.590 --> 00:33:06.190 line:80%
Mr. Li and my father
had been friends for years.

00:33:06.870 --> 00:33:08.270 line:80%
When my father was alive,

00:33:08.580 --> 00:33:10.960 line:80%
he often supported
our butcher shop's business.

00:33:10.960 --> 00:33:11.960 line:80%
I thought,

00:33:12.720 --> 00:33:14.310 line:80%
since Mr. Li is so nice,

00:33:14.770 --> 00:33:17.710 line:80%
his manager must be
a wonderful person, too.

00:33:20.350 --> 00:33:21.590 line:80%
Giving you the recipe

00:33:22.200 --> 00:33:24.110 line:80%
will allow the people of Lin'an Town

00:33:24.110 --> 00:33:26.260 line:80%
to taste the cooking
my parents left behind.

00:33:26.260 --> 00:33:28.730 line:80%
They'd surely be happy about it in heaven.

00:33:38.360 --> 00:33:39.280 line:80%
Come with me.

00:33:45.390 --> 00:33:46.070 line:80%
Look.

00:33:46.800 --> 00:33:47.870 line:80%
During the New Year,

00:33:47.870 --> 00:33:49.200 line:80%
my business is booming.

00:33:49.550 --> 00:33:51.200 line:80%
The banquets are fully booked.

00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:53.930 line:80%
So the demand for braised meat is
naturally high.

00:33:54.040 --> 00:33:56.420 line:80%
Those old gourmets are very picky diners.

00:33:56.550 --> 00:33:57.440 line:80%
How about this?

00:33:57.720 --> 00:34:00.760 line:80%
You supply the braised meat to us
for the New Year first,

00:34:00.760 --> 00:34:04.070 line:80%
and I'll figure out a way to fill the gap
after the New Year.

00:34:05.590 --> 00:34:07.410 line:80%
You'll need to buy a new house
in a new place.

00:34:07.410 --> 00:34:09.140 line:80%
That will cost a bunch of money.

00:34:09.470 --> 00:34:10.700 line:80%
I'll pay you extra.

00:34:10.780 --> 00:34:13.780 line:80%
Just help me get through
this end of the year smoothly.

00:34:15.610 --> 00:34:17.740 line:80%
This is indeed a good way to make money.

00:34:19.610 --> 00:34:21.530 line:80%
Thank you, Manager Yu.

00:34:22.120 --> 00:34:23.920 line:80%
I should be the one thanking you.

00:34:24.430 --> 00:34:25.870 line:80%
For the Wang's braised meat,

00:34:25.870 --> 00:34:27.200 line:80%
we used to buy it

00:34:27.240 --> 00:34:29.039 line:80%
at 40 wen a catty
regardless of the season.

00:34:29.039 --> 00:34:30.140 line:80%
With today's high meat prices

00:34:30.140 --> 00:34:31.740 line:80%
and your excellent quality,

00:34:31.890 --> 00:34:34.479 line:80%
I'll give you 50 wen.

00:34:34.840 --> 00:34:36.560 line:80%
From now on, you'll make braised meat
in the kitchen.

00:34:36.560 --> 00:34:37.959 line:80%
Wages will be paid daily.

00:34:38.600 --> 00:34:39.720 line:80%
That's too much.

00:34:39.720 --> 00:34:40.600 line:80%
It's not.

00:34:41.200 --> 00:34:42.470 line:80%
Generous in friendship,

00:34:42.470 --> 00:34:43.729 line:80%
exacting in business.

00:34:44.160 --> 00:34:45.140 line:80%
Tomorrow,

00:34:45.160 --> 00:34:47.689 line:80%
come over,
and I'll draw up a contract for you.

00:34:47.910 --> 00:34:49.430 line:80%
To show my sincerity,

00:34:49.600 --> 00:34:50.990 line:80%
I'm willing to pay a deposit first.

00:34:50.990 --> 00:34:51.630 line:80%
Fuling.

00:34:55.160 --> 00:34:56.560 line:80%
T-This won't do.

00:34:56.680 --> 00:34:57.720 line:80%
We haven't signed the contract,

00:34:57.720 --> 00:34:59.120 line:80%
and if I take your money now,

00:34:59.120 --> 00:35:00.440 line:80%
it wouldn't be right.

00:35:00.870 --> 00:35:03.000 line:80%
I'm afraid you'll go back on your word.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:04.620 line:80%
Just take it.

00:35:05.600 --> 00:35:06.430 line:80%
If you don't take it,

00:35:06.430 --> 00:35:07.890 line:80%
I won't feel at ease.

00:35:14.310 --> 00:35:15.780 line:80%
Then I accept.

00:35:16.210 --> 00:35:17.470 line:80%
Thank you, Manager Yu.

00:35:18.470 --> 00:35:20.930 line:80%
I'm happy today. So don't call me Manager.

00:35:21.690 --> 00:35:22.530 line:80%
Call me

00:35:23.610 --> 00:35:24.490 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:35:27.280 --> 00:35:28.480 line:80%
Thank you, Qianqian.

00:35:35.980 --> 00:35:39.370 line:80%
Manager! Come out!

00:35:39.400 --> 00:35:41.200 line:80%
Stop playing the pipa!

00:35:41.790 --> 00:35:44.240 line:80%
Chef Li, come out right now!

00:35:44.260 --> 00:35:46.380 line:80%
Guo, what are you doing?

00:35:46.410 --> 00:35:47.580 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:35:47.610 --> 00:35:50.020 line:80%
We only cooperated
because the Fan family had an incident.

00:35:50.020 --> 00:35:51.780 line:80%
Now it's the agreed date.

00:35:51.830 --> 00:35:52.910 line:80%
Don't you know that?

00:35:52.910 --> 00:35:54.960 line:80%
Bullshit!

00:35:55.950 --> 00:35:57.950 line:80%
When you were short of meat,
you came to me for help.

00:35:57.950 --> 00:35:59.560 line:80%
Now the little brat from the Fan family is

00:35:59.560 --> 00:36:01.350 line:80%
back, and you want
to kick me out right away?

00:36:01.350 --> 00:36:03.200 line:80%
I'm telling you, no way!

00:36:03.200 --> 00:36:04.910 line:80%
You're taking this meat today,

00:36:04.910 --> 00:36:06.870 line:80%
whether you like it or not!

00:36:07.510 --> 00:36:09.430 line:80%
Qianqian, this Guo is

00:36:09.460 --> 00:36:10.760 line:80%
selling water-injected meat.

00:36:10.760 --> 00:36:12.120 line:80%
He even added borax.

00:36:12.120 --> 00:36:13.830 line:80%
It looks fresh but tastes rotten.

00:36:13.830 --> 00:36:14.240 line:80%
Stop shouting!

00:36:14.240 --> 00:36:15.830 line:80%
He's notorious in our trade.

00:36:15.830 --> 00:36:16.870 line:80%
Get lost! Get out of here!

00:36:16.870 --> 00:36:20.760 line:80%
If you don't come out,
I'll spill the beans.

00:36:21.720 --> 00:36:23.910 line:80%
This Chef Li is

00:36:23.910 --> 00:36:27.950 line:80%
having an affair with Fan Changyu!

00:36:27.990 --> 00:36:28.770 line:80%
What...

00:36:28.830 --> 00:36:29.830 line:80%
Are you crazy?

00:36:29.830 --> 00:36:31.240 line:80%
How dare he slander me!

00:36:31.640 --> 00:36:34.600 line:80%
-My father scolded him a lot when he was alive.
-You're so old...

00:36:34.600 --> 00:36:35.350 line:80%
I'll go teach him a lesson for you.

00:36:35.350 --> 00:36:36.760 line:80%
-Shame on you!
-Changyu.

00:36:36.760 --> 00:36:37.910 line:80%
What should I say about you?

00:36:37.910 --> 00:36:39.430 line:80%
-Calm down.
-Should I say you're still potent,

00:36:39.430 --> 00:36:42.160 line:80%
-or you're still going strong?
-It's my turf.

00:36:42.190 --> 00:36:44.150 line:80%
-I got this.
-You're shameless!

00:36:45.870 --> 00:36:47.500 line:80%
Manager Yu!

00:36:47.640 --> 00:36:49.160 line:80%
If you don't come out now,

00:36:49.240 --> 00:36:51.770 line:80%
I'll spill more secrets!

00:36:51.790 --> 00:36:53.590 line:80%
-What's all the fuss?
-Get down!

00:36:55.280 --> 00:36:55.950 line:80%
Manager.

00:36:56.350 --> 00:36:57.830 line:80%
It's you, Butcher Guo.

00:36:58.430 --> 00:37:00.160 line:80%
We're open for business.

00:37:00.160 --> 00:37:01.030 line:80%
With you making such a scene,

00:37:01.030 --> 00:37:03.030 line:80%
how am I supposed to run my business?

00:37:03.760 --> 00:37:05.950 line:80%
Manager Yu, you finally came out.

00:37:08.470 --> 00:37:10.370 line:80%
It's a small world for enemies.

00:37:12.160 --> 00:37:13.450 line:80%
Manager Yu,

00:37:13.720 --> 00:37:15.720 line:80%
your people are

00:37:16.080 --> 00:37:18.950 line:80%
only doing these sneaky,

00:37:18.950 --> 00:37:21.600 line:80%
dirty, shameless things.

00:37:21.600 --> 00:37:22.240 line:80%
Are you going to handle it?

00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:23.900 line:80%
Still talking nonsense here!

00:37:24.430 --> 00:37:26.900 line:80%
Butcher Guo, you make it sound so real.

00:37:27.040 --> 00:37:29.600 line:80%
Did you hide under the bed
and see it yourself?

00:37:29.600 --> 00:37:30.560 line:80%
Did you see it?

00:37:33.160 --> 00:37:35.120 line:80%
I suggest you, Manager Yu,

00:37:35.120 --> 00:37:37.070 line:80%
give me an explanation today.

00:37:37.470 --> 00:37:39.560 line:80%
Advisor Guo is

00:37:40.950 --> 00:37:42.840 line:80%
my uncle.

00:37:43.990 --> 00:37:47.250 line:80%
If I report this to my uncle,

00:37:47.430 --> 00:37:48.390 line:80%
Manager Yu,

00:37:48.390 --> 00:37:51.310 line:80%
you'll be in deep trouble.

00:37:52.710 --> 00:37:54.000 line:80%
What a coincidence.

00:37:54.430 --> 00:37:57.470 line:80%
Advisor Guo is drinking tea
in the private room in the back right now.

00:37:57.470 --> 00:37:59.350 line:80%
Why don't we go ask him to judge?

00:38:02.470 --> 00:38:03.350 line:80%
Really?

00:38:04.030 --> 00:38:06.350 line:80%
Alright, let's go then.

00:38:09.670 --> 00:38:11.350 line:80%
Take the meat.

00:38:14.010 --> 00:38:16.260 line:80%
Guys, throw the meat out immediately.

00:38:17.010 --> 00:38:18.730 line:80%
It's fine now. It's fine.

00:38:18.750 --> 00:38:20.000 line:80%
Music, please.

00:38:20.240 --> 00:38:22.740 line:80%
There will be singing
and dancing for the vibe soon.

00:38:22.740 --> 00:38:23.780 line:80%
Everyone, relax.

00:38:23.810 --> 00:38:25.340 line:80%
Enjoy your food and drinks.

00:38:31.580 --> 00:38:32.290 line:80%
This way.

00:38:37.700 --> 00:38:38.290 line:80%
Please.

00:38:42.600 --> 00:38:44.850 line:80%
Uncle? Are you inside?

00:38:45.110 --> 00:38:46.550 line:80%
Screw you inside!

00:38:47.870 --> 00:38:48.430 line:80%
On my turf,

00:38:48.430 --> 00:38:50.230 line:80%
how dare you, a nobody, run wild?

00:38:50.310 --> 00:38:52.150 line:80%
I'm going to tear you apart today!

00:38:52.150 --> 00:38:53.170 line:80%
Manager,

00:38:53.310 --> 00:38:54.680 line:80%
your mink coat is expensive.

00:38:54.680 --> 00:38:56.280 line:80%
Maybe let's stay out of this?

00:38:56.390 --> 00:38:57.030 line:80%
Right.

00:38:57.030 --> 00:38:58.280 line:80%
I almost forgot.

00:39:03.030 --> 00:39:04.910 line:80%
Changyu, did that scare you?

00:39:06.680 --> 00:39:07.940 line:80%
Just rough him up a bit.

00:39:07.990 --> 00:39:08.950 line:80%
Don't kill him.

00:39:08.950 --> 00:39:09.640 line:80%
Got it.

00:39:09.950 --> 00:39:11.720 line:80%
Let's go.
There's nothing interesting to see here.

00:39:11.720 --> 00:39:13.720 line:80%
Not as exciting as butchering pigs.

00:39:16.200 --> 00:39:16.960 line:80%
Beat him up!

00:39:18.870 --> 00:39:19.990 line:80%
Not the face!

00:39:19.990 --> 00:39:21.160 line:80%
You know what?

00:39:21.160 --> 00:39:22.240 line:80%
We have a show up ahead.

00:39:22.240 --> 00:39:23.030 line:80%
It's amazing.

00:39:23.030 --> 00:39:25.030 line:80%
Come on, I'll take you to have a look.

00:40:04.540 --> 00:40:05.740 line:80%
My Lord, please look.

00:40:05.970 --> 00:40:08.170 line:80%
It's that young lady from the other day.

00:40:08.700 --> 00:40:10.700 line:80%
Well, just the one who lost her shoe.

00:40:10.830 --> 00:40:11.980 line:80%
Her name is Fan Changyu.

00:40:11.980 --> 00:40:15.190 line:80%
We searched everywhere,
yet it turns out that we had already met.

00:40:15.190 --> 00:40:16.410 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:40:19.680 --> 00:40:21.380 line:80%
Tell the spies in Lin'an
to keep a close watch.

00:40:21.380 --> 00:40:22.910 line:80%
And those Suicide Warriors, too.

00:40:22.910 --> 00:40:24.540 line:80%
Don't alert the magistrate yet.

00:40:24.540 --> 00:40:26.540 line:80%
I want to meet the coroner in person.

00:40:26.630 --> 00:40:27.360 line:80%
Understood.

00:40:38.200 --> 00:40:39.300 line:80%
Changyu, you're back.

00:40:39.300 --> 00:40:40.140 line:80%
Yeah, hello.

00:40:42.680 --> 00:40:43.410 line:80%
Changyu.

00:40:47.160 --> 00:40:48.390 line:80%
I'm back!

00:40:49.390 --> 00:40:50.280 line:80%
Changyu.

00:40:50.870 --> 00:40:51.470 line:80%
Come on.

00:40:54.140 --> 00:40:54.760 line:80%
Look.

00:40:55.770 --> 00:40:58.040 line:80%
Are these all for Changning?

00:40:58.120 --> 00:40:59.870 line:80%
For Changning and Zheng.

00:41:00.080 --> 00:41:01.200 line:80%
Zheng hates bitter medicine.

00:41:01.200 --> 00:41:02.600 line:80%
So do you.

00:41:03.640 --> 00:41:04.370 line:80%
You're back.

00:41:04.570 --> 00:41:05.240 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao.

00:41:05.240 --> 00:41:07.040 line:80%
You bought so much. What is this?

00:41:07.690 --> 00:41:10.100 line:80%
So much candy! Is it New Year's Eve?

00:41:10.510 --> 00:41:12.160 line:80%
I went to the Yixiang Restaurant
for a deal.

00:41:12.160 --> 00:41:13.560 line:80%
Yu Qianqian gave it to me.

00:41:13.670 --> 00:41:15.020 line:80%
That Manager Yu?

00:41:15.970 --> 00:41:18.320 line:80%
I didn't expect her to be so nice.

00:41:19.470 --> 00:41:20.470 line:80%
A woman running

00:41:20.470 --> 00:41:22.830 line:80%
2 restaurants
in both the county and Lin'an.

00:41:22.830 --> 00:41:23.830 line:80%
Very impressive.

00:41:23.990 --> 00:41:25.120 line:80%
You know her, too?

00:41:25.240 --> 00:41:26.350 line:80%
Of course.

00:41:26.870 --> 00:41:29.000 line:80%
She came to Lin'an pregnant back then,

00:41:29.830 --> 00:41:30.870 line:80%
with no relatives to turn to.

00:41:30.870 --> 00:41:32.600 line:80%
She was even worse off than you.

00:41:32.720 --> 00:41:33.920 line:80%
Where is her husband?

00:41:34.470 --> 00:41:35.600 line:80%
I don't know.

00:41:35.600 --> 00:41:36.990 line:80%
He must be capable.

00:41:36.990 --> 00:41:38.030 line:80%
Otherwise, how could he marry

00:41:38.030 --> 00:41:39.390 line:80%
such a capable woman?

00:41:58.830 --> 00:42:00.530 line:80%
Changning is sleeping here in my place.

00:42:00.530 --> 00:42:02.530 line:80%
Why don't you go back to hit the sack?

00:42:04.160 --> 00:42:06.360 line:80%
I'll roast the persimmons a bit longer.

00:42:06.430 --> 00:42:08.220 line:80%
The persimmon tree isn't falling.

00:42:08.220 --> 00:42:10.820 line:80%
You can roast persimmons
anytime in your life.

00:42:11.120 --> 00:42:14.580 line:80%
But are you going to avoid
consummating the marriage forever?

00:42:19.940 --> 00:42:22.070 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, Yan Zheng and I actually...

00:42:23.470 --> 00:42:24.280 line:80%
Didn't you say Yan Zheng

00:42:24.280 --> 00:42:25.830 line:80%
agreed to leave with you?

00:42:26.470 --> 00:42:29.030 line:80%
He said he would leave with me for now.

00:42:29.830 --> 00:42:30.870 line:80%
But what about the future?

00:42:30.870 --> 00:42:32.400 line:80%
Why worry about the future?

00:42:33.310 --> 00:42:34.160 line:80%
Since he married into your family,

00:42:34.160 --> 00:42:35.920 line:80%
you have to take the initiative.

00:42:35.920 --> 00:42:37.810 line:80%
No matter what's on your mind,

00:42:38.380 --> 00:42:41.100 line:80%
I think Yan Zheng is
a wonderful young man.

00:42:41.430 --> 00:42:43.890 line:80%
Look at the huge trouble
your family ran into this time.

00:42:43.890 --> 00:42:46.810 line:80%
He went to save Changning
despite all his injuries.

00:42:46.870 --> 00:42:47.430 line:80%
Also,

00:42:47.950 --> 00:42:49.030 line:80%
at the county government office court,

00:42:49.030 --> 00:42:50.950 line:80%
if Mr. Sun hadn't arrived in time,

00:42:51.140 --> 00:42:54.340 line:80%
he really would have
gone all out to fight the magistrate.

00:42:56.510 --> 00:42:58.350 line:80%
With such a responsible man,

00:42:58.430 --> 00:43:00.310 line:80%
why don't you seize the opportunity

00:43:00.310 --> 00:43:01.800 line:80%
to get things fully done?

00:43:02.120 --> 00:43:03.390 line:80%
Once you sleep together,

00:43:03.390 --> 00:43:04.870 line:80%
his heart will be with you.

00:43:06.720 --> 00:43:09.430 line:80%
If I just go consummate the marriage
with him for no reason,

00:43:09.430 --> 00:43:10.680 line:80%
what would that make me?

00:43:10.680 --> 00:43:12.950 line:80%
He's your husband. What's wrong with that?

00:43:12.950 --> 00:43:15.150 line:80%
Do you need to pick a lucky date for that?

00:43:15.390 --> 00:43:16.310 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao.

00:43:17.760 --> 00:43:18.800 line:80%
Fine.

00:43:19.510 --> 00:43:21.170 line:80%
Let me give you another trick.

00:43:22.470 --> 00:43:24.890 line:80%
During the day, I washed the bedding

00:43:25.350 --> 00:43:27.280 line:80%
you used on the floor in your house.

00:43:28.780 --> 00:43:31.910 line:80%
He won't bear to see you
sleep on the bare floor, would he?

00:44:02.230 --> 00:44:03.130 line:80%
Come here.